# Jojo OS — environment example
#
# Jojo OS does NOT read API keys from this file. Provider keys are added in the
# app (API Keys page) and encrypted with your OS keychain. This file exists only
# for optional local dev/build settings and as a template for MCP servers.
#
# Copy to `.env` (git-ignored) if you need any of these. NEVER commit real secrets.

# Example only — real provider keys go in the app, not here:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# Generated MCP servers get their own .env.example inside their folder.
